---
title: Stir-Fried Pork Noodles with Green Beans and Cashews
description: Sticky and sweet hoisin sauce is just the thing for this flavourful meal. We’ve kept your bowl packed full of fresh flavours with green beans and cilantro. The crowning jewels of this dish are the roasted cashews, adding a delightful crunch to an easy weeknight stunner.
